===Noun===
'''Cartesian coordinates''' ''plural''

#(''mathematics'') The [[coordinate]]s of a point measured as its [[perpendicular distance]] to the right of a vertical axis (the [[y-axis|''y''-axis]]) and its perpendicular distance above a horizontal axis (the [[x-axis|''x''-axis]]).

